dataJson.description: Semester 1 group project for VIA University. Built using JavaFx.
dataJson.name: Hotel booking system
dataJson.story: The first semester group project we had at VIA. The task was to build a booking system for a hotel that was using an old ledger. No database was required so the data was stored in binary files as serialized Java Objects. This was a group project and I had 3 team members
